Hi, I have standard maps on the server where I have the levels, here is the full level all the de_dust2 maps that I came up with a long time ago. 
I made a complete map for bhop, with alphabet blocks. 

That is, you need to find part of the alphabet that would go completely map. 
Alphabet contain A B C D E, you need to collect all the sections to go to the end. 
I also placed a bonus on the map that contains A B C. 

The color orange says that you should touch this color;
The color blue says that there is an invisible wall; 
The color purple says that you need to collect a letter to go further;
The color of yellow says that this is a bonus level.

I think everything is clear and simple. Good luck in passing!
